amily: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">研究所：碳基电子学研究中心</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;\">研究领域：纳米电子学</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">邮件：</span>yu_cao[at]pku.edu.cn</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">教育背景：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2008.9-2012.7 </span><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">北京大学</span> <span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">微电子学学士，经济学学士（双学位）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">2012.8-2017.5 </span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">美国南加利福尼亚大学</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">电子工程博士</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">工作履历：</strong></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">2017.6-2018.6 </span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">美国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">Intel</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">公司</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">逻辑技术研发部（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">Ronler Acres Campus</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">）</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">研发工程师</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">2018.6-2021.3 </span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">中国科学院空间应用工程与技术中心</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">电子信息室</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">副研究员</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">2021.3-</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">至今</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">北京大学碳基电子学研究中心</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">副研究员</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height:150%\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">代表性学术论著：</strong></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">1) </span>Lin, Y.;<strong>Cao, Y.</strong>;Ding, S.;Zhang, P.;Xu, L.;Liu, C.;Hu, Q.;Jin, C.;Peng, L.-M.; Zhang, Z. Scaling aligned carbon nanotube transistors to a sub-10 nm node. <em>Nature Electronics</em> <strong>2023</strong>, <em>6</em>, 506-515.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">2) Zhu, X.;Xi, M.;Wang, J.;Zhang, P.;Li, Y.;Luo, X.;Bai, L.;Chen, X.;Peng, L. M.;<strong>Cao, Y.</strong>;Li, Q.; Liang, X. High-performance ternary logic circuits and neural networks based on carbon nanotube source-gating transistors. <em>Science Advances</em> <strong>2025</strong>, 11, eadt1909.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">3) </span>S. Li, Z. Yin, Y. Li, X. Dong, T. Luo, M. Xi, L. Bai, X. Cao, X. Liang, Y. Cao, Dielectric and passivation layer optimization in carbon nanotube thin-film transistors for display driving applications, <em>Carbon</em><strong> 2025</strong>, 237, 120154</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">4) Bai, L.; Lin, Y.; Chen, X.; Yin, H.; Jin, C.; Wang, Y.; Zhang, Z.; Peng, L. M.; Liang, X.;<strong> Cao, Y.</strong> Achieving High-Performance Polymer-Wrapper-Free Aligned Carbon Nanotube Field-Effect Transistors through Degradable Polymer Wrapping and Efficient Removal Techniques. <em>ACS Nano</em><strong> 2024</strong>, 18 (34), 23392-23402.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">5) Xi, M.;Liu, F.;Zhu, X.;Li, Y.;Bai, L.;Chen, X.;Gong, Y.;Guo, Y.;Zhou, Y.;Peng, L.;Kang, J.;<strong>Cao, Y.</strong>; Liang, X. High-performance thin-film transistors based on aligned carbon nanotubes for mini- and micro-LED displays. <em>Carbon</em> <strong>2024</strong>, 218, 118718.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">6) Liu, C.<strong>;Cao, Y.</strong>;Lu, H.;Lin, Y.;Jin, C.; Zhang, Z. Scaling of N-Type Field-Effect Transistors Based on Aligned Carbon Nanotube Arrays. <em>ACS Applied Materials &amp; Interfaces</em> <strong>2024</strong>, 16, 41, 55964–55969.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">7) </span>Lin, Y.;<strong>Cao, Y.</strong>;Lu, H.;Liu, C.;Zhang, Z.;Jin, C.;Peng, L.-M.; Zhang, Z. Improving the Performance of Aligned Carbon Nanotube-Based Transistors by Refreshing the Substrate Surface. <em>ACS Applied Materials &amp; Interfaces</em> <strong>2023</strong>, <em>15</em>, 10830-10837.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">8) </span>Liu, C.;<strong>Cao, Y.</strong>;Wang, B.;Zhang, Z.;Lin, Y.;Xu, L.;Yang, Y.;Jin, C.;Peng, L. M.; Zhang, Z. Complementary Transistors Based on Aligned Semiconducting Carbon Nanotube Arrays. <em>ACS Nano</em> <strong>2022</strong>, <em>16</em>, 21482-21490.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">9) Liu, F., Chen, X., Liu, H. et al. High-yield and low-cost separation of high-purity semiconducting single-walled carbon nanotubes with closed-loop recycling of raw materials and solvents. <em>Nano Research</em> <strong>2021</strong>, 14, 4281–4287.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%; font-size: 14px;\">10) Liu, F.; Chen, X.; Liu, H.; Zhao, J.; Xi, M.; Xiao, H.; Lu, T.; <strong>Cao, Y.</strong>; Li, Y.; Peng, L.; et al. High-Yield and Low-Cost Separation of High-Purity Semiconducting Single-Walled Carbon Nanotubes with Closed-Loop Recycling of Raw Materials and Solvents. <em>Nano Res.</em> <strong>2021</strong>, 14 (11), 4281-4287.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:24px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">11) </span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">《中国新材料产业发展报告（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">2022</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">）》，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">8</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">章，《半导体碳纳米管》，<strong>曹宇</strong>，张志勇，彭练矛，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%;\">ISBN 978-7-122-43509-5</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;\">。</span></span></p>\n<p style